CEM_enUS1118US1118&amp;oq=Imperial+Star+405+Watt+Solar+Panel&amp;gs_lcrp=EgZjaHJvbWUyBggAEEUYOTIHCAEQIRigATIHCAIQIRigATIHCAMQIRigATIHCAQQIRigATIHCAUQIRigAdIBBzIxM2owajeoAgCwAgA&amp;sourceid=chrome&amp;ie=UTF-8&amp;mstk=AUtExfDB-f05KLs1GDRu_LyftXxpztZMp4nYKbmgAH7ObJ3xrFD267ABLcGuNjC3lq8RUXceerpmV4rpu2UtfAworLcuzEYZl0OmWY5I9hI3YdhmtCauwhE-KgFWC2NwCXwvkORqZMlrkey6N9-jX-i_AXOFiHWd_Jl15715Czp4TwIuopsx-k60hbdTDmC-IZwBsImBkYJWzie7o_VHkiM58FmDEYl3n6PxIrlTWET35g0SrHIPaGu7wTEpqHxX-8Gr5Asf3rfy7xWHfyRtQp6ffteb&amp;csui=3&amp;ved=2ahUKEwiHw8jvzYqQAxUyDkQIHfNiMkMQgK4QegQIARAE\">ORION</a> series, which use different cell technologies like PERC and TOPCon.</p><p>They offer features like high efficiency, weather resistance, and a long lifespan, with Imperial Star Solar providing customization options for residential, commercial, and industrial projects.&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Key Characteristics:</strong></p><ul><li><p><strong>Manufacturer: </strong>Imperial Star Solar&nbsp;</p></li><li><p><strong>Power Output:</strong>405 watts&nbsp;</p></li><li><p><strong>Dimensions: </strong>45 x 68 x 1.5 inches</p></li></ul><p><strong>Applications and Use Cases:</strong></p><ul><li><p><strong>Residential and Commercial Projects: </strong>Customizable options are available for diverse energy needs, blending seamlessly with various environments.&nbsp;</p></li><li><p><strong>Utility-Scale Applications: </strong>The high power output and advanced features make them suitable for large-scale projects.&nbsp;</p></li><li><p><strong>Off-Grid and Recreational Needs: </strong>While a single panel won\'t power a whole home, 405W panels are well-suited for smaller, low-to-moderate energy needs, such as charging electronics or powering lighting.&nbsp;</p></li></ul>',99.00,NULL,'/uploads/datasheets/1761228845838-tkhe28i6e4d.pdf','a0b3eb1a-4e72-11f0-bbc5-06479488ad4b','ISM7-SHDD108-405/M',0.00,'[{\"type\":\"fixed\",\"name\":\"Standard Shipping\",\"description\":\"3-5 business days\",\"cost\":60},{\"type\":\"local_pickup\",\"name\":\"Local Pickup\",\"description\":\"Pick up from our location\",\"warehouse_ids\":[\"main-warehouse-id\",\"41ee39d4-51d5-11f0-bbc5-06479488ad4b\",\"east-warehouse-id\"]}]',0,'calculated',0.00,'imperial-star-405-watt-solar-panel-ism7-shdd108-405m',1,'2025-10-04 13:02:52','2025-11-14 23:31:50'),('77c0ad41-51f8-11f0-bbc5-06479488ad4b','Sunpower 435 Watt Solar Panel','<p>Monocrystalline solar cell technology for enhanced efficiency</p><p>Produces 20.4W per square feet to optimize larger roof spaces</p><p>Independently generates renewable energy for electric bill savings</p>',90.00,NULL,'/uploads/datasheets/1751916378893-fsb2ke3n99.pdf','a0b3eb1a-4e72-11f0-bbc5-06479488ad4b','SPR-435NE-WHT-D',0.00,'[{\"type\":\"fixed\",\"name\":\"Standard Shipping\",\"description\":\"3-5 business days\",\"cost\":500},{\"type\":\"local_pickup\",\"name\":\"Local Pickup\",\"description\":\"Pick up from our location\",\"warehouse_ids\":[\"east-warehouse-id\",\"main-warehouse-id\",\"41ee39d4-51d5-11f0-bbc5-06479488ad4b\"]}]',0,'calculated',0.00,'sunpower-435-watt-solar-panel-spr-435ne-wht-d',0,'2025-06-25 19:13:25','2025-10-03 12:23:18'),('78b938ed-7340-11f0-9985-0637a5b9918d','SolarEdge 340W 1000V PV Solar Panel Power Optimizer P340','',25.00,NULL,NULL,'b5ef143e-4e72-11f0-bbc5-06479488ad4b','P340-5NM4MRS',0.00,'[]',0,'calculated',0.00,'solaredge-340w-1000v-pv-solar-panel-power-optimizer-p340-p340-5nm4mrs',1,'2025-08-07 03:41:58','2025-08-23 12:41:24'),('79d5aa62-520f-11f0-bbc5-06479488ad4b','Growatt 3.8 kW Hybrid Inverter','<p>Empower your home with clean, reliable energy with the <strong>Growatt 3.8kW MIN 3800TL-XH-US Hybrid Inverter</strong>. This cutting-edge inverter is designed for the modern energy-efficient home, offering seamless integration with battery storage for a flexible and robust solar power system.</p><p><strong>Key Features:</strong></p><ul><li><p><strong>Hybrid Power:</strong> Supports both grid-tie and battery storage applications, allowing you to maximize your solar energy usage and enjoy reliable backup power.</p></li><li><p><strong>High Efficiency:</strong> With a peak efficiency of 98% and a CEC weighted efficiency of 97% at 240V, the MIN 3800TL-XH-US ensures you get the most out of your solar panels.</p></li><li><p><strong>Battery-Ready:</strong> Flexible integration with both DC coupled and AC coupled battery systems, providing versatility in choosing your energy storage solution.</p></li><li><p><strong>Smart Energy Management:</strong> Features an Integrated Energy Management System (EMS) that supports various energy management modes, including self-consumption, zero export, time-of-use (TOU), and off-grid operation.</p></li><li><p><strong>Reliable Backup Power:</strong> Offers backup power and dark start operations, ensuring your energy needs are met even during power outages.</p></li><li><p><strong>Enhanced Safety:</strong> Equipped with rapid shutdown and AFCI integration for increased safety and peace of mind.</p></li><li><p><strong>Smart Connectivity:</strong> Integrated WiFi and LAN communication modules, along with Tigo Transmitter, enable seamless monitoring and management of your system. You can easily access IoT integrated cloud services and monitor your system through the intuitive mobile app.</p></li><li><p><strong>Dual MPPT Tracking:</strong> Features dual MPPT trackers, optimizing solar energy harvest from multiple roof orientations or varying panel conditions.</p></li><li><p><strong>Robust and Durable:</strong> Designed with natural convection cooling and a NEMA4X (IP65) rated enclosure, ensuring durability and less maintenance.</p></li><li><p><strong>Compliance:</strong> Meets key standards, including UL1741SA, CA Rule 21 &amp; HECO, ensuring seamless integration and compliance with regulatory requirements.</p></li><li><p><strong>Comprehensive Warranty:</strong> Backed by a 10-year warranty, with options for extended coverage, providing long-term reliability and peace of mind.</p></li></ul><p>The Growatt MIN 3800TL-XH-US offers high performance and a cost-effective solution for residential solar energy systems. It is compatible with Growatt ARO/APX HV batteries and designed to meet the evolving needs of the renewable energy industry. Whether you are looking to go off-grid, stay connected to the grid, or achieve a combination of both, this inverter provides the flexibility and reliability to meet your specific energy storage needs.</p>',400.00,NULL,'/uploads/datasheets/1750889274964-adwy9s0c0i.pdf','b5ef143e-4e72-11f0-bbc5-06479488ad4b','MIN 3800TL-XH-US',0.00,'[]',0,'calculated',0.00,'growatt-38-kw-hybrid-inverter-min-3800tl-xh-us',1,'2025-06-25 21:58:07','2025-08-04 19:29:55'),('7b8f63a5-b008-11f0-8e1b-0637a5b9918d','Tigo Solar Module Optimizer With 1.2m MC4 Cables','<h3 style=\"text-align: center\">Tigo TS4-A-O Module Level Optimizer</h3><p><strong>NOTE: Tigo TS4-A-F can be used with TS4-A-2F but cannot be used with TS4-A-M, TS4-A-S, TS4-A-0 units due to different communication architectures.</strong></p><p>Part number: 461-00252-32<br>Comes with 1.2 meter MC4 connector cables.</p><p>Optimization is a Flex MLPE function available as an integrated modular junction box base (TS4-O) or as an add-on unit (TS4-A-O). Design using unequal string lengths, mixed orientations, or areas of mismatch. Install in shaded areas with a reduced setback ratio. In addition to optimization, the TS4-A-O enables module level monitoring, and rapid shutdown in compliance with NEC 2014, 2017, 2020.</p><p><strong>Features and Benefits:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Higher performance optimizer with Predictive IV Technology (PIV)</p></li><li><p>The ONLY optimizer with selective deployment</p></li><li><p>Includes the benefits of Safety &amp; Monitoring</p></li><li><p>Meets US NEC rapid shutdown requirements</p></li><li><p>Optimizes right out of the box</p></li><li><p>Shade and age tolerance to maximize lifetime yield</p></li><li><p>Works wirelessly with the TAP &amp; CCA</p></li><li><p>Configuration: 1 module per TS4</p></li><li><p>Required components: Cloud Connect Advanced (CCA) and Tigo Access Point (TAP)</p></li></ul>',55.00,NULL,'/uploads/datasheets/1761221090319-78034f2zpn3.pdf','b5ef143e-4e72-11f0-bbc5-06479488ad4b','TS4-A-O',0.00,'[{\"type\":\"local_pickup\",\"name\":\"Local Pickup\",\"description\":\"Pick up from our location\",\"warehouse_ids\":[\"main-warehouse-id\"]},{\"type\":\"free\",\"name\":\"Standard Shipping\",\"description\":\"3-5 business days\"}]',0,'calculated',0.00,'tigo-solar-module-optimizer-with-12m-mc4-cables-ts4-a-o',1,'2025-10-23 12:04:52','2025-10-23 12:10:15'),('81174ebb-60e5-11f0-8e60-0637a5b9918d','APsystems AC Bus Trunk Cable','<p>The APSystems AC-3-35A-F is a female three-phase AC bus trunk cable connector used in APsystems solar installations to connect microinverters (such as those from the YC600/QS1 or DS3 series) to the main AC trunk cable. This connector is rated for 35A and is designed to be used with a corresponding male connector to complete the electrical connection in a three-phase system, allowing for efficient and reliable power distribution from the microinverters to the grid</p><h3>Specifications</h3><ul><li><p><strong>Voltage rating</strong>: 600 VAC.</p></li><li><p><strong>Current rating</strong>: 35 A.</p></li><li><p><strong>Wiring</strong>: 3-phase configuration.</p><ul><li><p>Black: L1</p></li><li><p>Red: L2</p></li><li><p>Blue: L3</p></li></ul></li><li><p><strong>Length and connectors</strong>: The cable comes in a series with up to 60 connectors, with a spacing of 2,400mm (approximately 7.8 feet) between each.</p></li><li><p><strong>Conductor resistance</strong>: 3.4090/km.</p></li><li><p><strong>Insulation resistance voltage</strong>: AC 2500V, 50mA for 1 minute.&nbsp;</p></li></ul><h3>Compatibility</h3><p>The AC-3-35A-F is typically used with APsystems 3-phase microinverters, such as the QT2 series, which are designed for 208V or 480V three-phase systems.&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Usage notes</strong></p><ul><li><p>It is crucial to use the correct end caps and sealing accessories with this trunk cable to maintain its weather-resistant properties.</p></li><li><p>For safety, you should turn off the AC bus and the grid before installation to prevent electric shock.&nbsp;</p></li></ul>',30.00,NULL,NULL,'b5ef143e-4e72-11f0-bbc5-06479488ad4b','AC-3-35A-F',0.00,'[]',0,'calculated',0.00,'apsystems-ac-bus-trunk-cable-ac-3-35a-f',1,'2025-07-14 19:05:27','2025-10-24 04:04:48'),('81edb507-6108-11f0-8e60-0637a5b9918d','Enphase Q-12-20-200 Portrait Trunk Cable','',8.00,NULL,NULL,'b5ef143e-4e72-11f0-bbc5-06479488ad4b','	Enphase Q-12-20-200',0.00,'[{\"type\":\"fixed\",\"name\":\"Standard Shipping\",\"description\":\"3-5 business days\",\"cost\":9.99},{\"type\":\"local_pickup\",\"name\":\"Local Pickup\",\"description\":\"Pick up from our location\",\"warehouse_ids\":[\"main-warehouse-id\"]}]',0,'calculated',0.00,'enphase-q-12-20-200-portrait-trunk-cable-enphase-q-12-20-200',1,'2025-07-14 23:16:01','2025-10-24 04:04:33'),('86f79a46-b5dc-11f0-8f67-0637a5b9918d','Mixed Clear 350-400 Watt Solar Panel','<p>These are various solar panels</p><table class=\"table-auto border-collapse border border-gray-300\" style=\"min-width: 100px\"><colgroup><col style=\"min-width: 25px\"><col style=\"min-width: 25px\"><col style=\"min-width: 25px\"><col style=\"min-width: 25px\"></colgroup><tbody><tr class=\"\"><td class=\"border border-gray-300 p-2\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p><strong>Panel</strong></p></td><td class=\"border border-gray-300 p-2\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p><strong>Condition</strong></p></td><td class=\"border border-gray-300 p-2\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p><strong>Quantity</strong></p></td><td class=\"border border-gray-300 p-2\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p><strong>Price Per Panel</strong></p></td></tr><tr class=\"\"><td class=\"border border-gray-300 p-2\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p>JA Solar 395</p></td><td class=\"border border-gray-300 p-2\" colspan=\"1\