efef7-4d16-11f0-bbc5-06479488ad4b','Solarever 455 Watt Solar Panel','',80.00,NULL,'/uploads/datasheets/1750493759477-gv5z5doo9le.pdf','a0b3eb1a-4e72-11f0-bbc5-06479488ad4b','SE-166*83-455M-144',0.00,'[]',0,'calculated',0.00,'solarever-455-watt-solar-panel-se-16683-455m-144',0,'2025-06-19 14:06:06','2025-07-02 18:27:29'),('8fee9700-d640-11f0-9a7d-064879f80623','Deep Unistrut 10 Foot Aluminum','<p>Deep Unistrut 10 Foot Silver Slotted Aluminum Strut Channel</p>',30.00,NULL,NULL,'be84ed54-4e72-11f0-bbc5-06479488ad4b','DEEPUNISTRUT',0.00,'[{\"type\":\"local_pickup\",\"name\":\"Local Pickup\",\"description\":\"Pick up from our location\",\"warehouse_ids\":[\"main-warehouse-id\"]}]',0,'calculated',0.00,'deep-unistrut-10-foot-aluminum-deepunistrut',1,'2025-12-11 03:22:02','2025-12-11 03:25:51'),('906f2c13-6aa8-11f0-8da0-0637a5b9918d','Tricky 1600 Watt Kit w/ Monitoring And Panels','<p>This kit will get you started with 1600 watts for your house.  It outputs 240 volts, so you can hook it into an electrical panel, your air conditioning unit, a dryer outlet, etc.  It also includes the ECU-R unit, so you can monitor how much power you are producing from each microinverter.</p>',990.00,NULL,NULL,'f1311ab6-6aa8-11f0-8da0-0637a5b9918d','trick-bundle-1600-monitoring-panels',0.00,'[{\"type\":\"local_pickup\",\"name\":\"Local Pickup\",\"description\":\"Pick up from our location\",\"warehouse_ids\":[\"main-warehouse-id\"]}]',1,'fixed',0.00,'tricky-1600-watt-kit-w-monitoring-and-panels-trick-bundle-1600-monitoring-panels',1,'2025-07-27 05:14:25','2025-08-06 05:40:51'),('9656ac5b-78af-11f0-8e76-0637a5b9918d','SolarEdge Cellular Plug-in Kit w/ Antenna','',60.00,NULL,NULL,'b5ef143e-4e72-11f0-bbc5-06479488ad4b','CELL-B-R05-US-H-S2',0.00,'[]',0,'calculated',0.00,'solaredge-cellular-plug-in-kit-w-antenna-cell-b-r05-us-h-s2',1,'2025-08-14 01:39:58','2025-08-14 01:39:58'),('9be158f1-9b38-11f0-8dbb-0637a5b9918d','MC4 Wire','',30.00,NULL,NULL,'b5ef143e-4e72-11f0-bbc5-06479488ad4b','MC4-WIRE',0.00,'[{\"type\":\"local_pickup\",\"name\":\"Local Pickup\",\"description\":\"Pick up from our location\",\"warehouse_ids\":[\"main-warehouse-id\"]}]',0,'calculated',0.00,'mc4-wire-mc4-wire',1,'2025-09-27 00:26:28','2025-11-15 11:19:57'),('a4d0bb03-5dcc-11f0-8e5b-0637a5b9918d','APsystems ECU-R Communications Gateway','<p>The Apsystems ECU-R Communications Gateway is an essential component for monitoring and managing solar energy systems. Manufactured by Apsystems, a pioneer in renewable energy solutions, this gateway offers advanced features and reliability to optimize solar power generation.</p><h2><strong>Special Features</strong></h2><ul><li><p>Seamless communication integration</p></li><li><p>Real-time monitoring capabilities</p></li><li><p>Wireless Wi-Fi connectivity</p></li><li><p>Compatibility with standard ECU units</p></li><li><p>Remote management and troubleshooting</p></li></ul><h2><strong>Technology and Overview</strong></h2><p>The Apsystems ECU-R Communications Gateway employs cutting-edge technology to facilitate seamless communication between solar energy systems and monitoring platforms. With its robust design, it ensures reliable data transmission and real-time monitoring of system performance.</p><h2><strong>Installation and Compatibility</strong></h2><p>Installation of the ECU-R gateway is straightforward, requiring minimal setup time. It is compatible with standard ECU units, allowing for easy integration into existing solar energy systems. The gateway\'s wireless Wi-Fi connectivity simplifies installation by eliminating the need for complex wiring.</p><h2><strong>Benefits and Applications</strong></h2><p>The ECU-R Communications Gateway offers numerous benefits, including cost-saving through efficient monitoring and maintenance of solar energy systems, reduced environmental impact by optimizing energy production, and versatile applications across residential, commercial, and industrial sectors.</p><h2><strong>Product Specifications</strong></h2><p>Model: ECU-R</p><p>Communication: Wi-Fi</p><p>Monitoring: Real-time</p><p>Compatibility: Standard ECU</p><p>Remote Management: Yes</p><p>Installation: Straightforward</p><p>Connectivity: Wireless</p><p>Applications: Residential, Commercial, Industrial</p>',160.00,NULL,'/uploads/datasheets/1752179551714-lfv4q2ehanm.pdf','b5ef143e-4e72-11f0-bbc5-06479488ad4b','ECU-R',0.00,'[{\"type\":\"fixed\",\"name\":\"Standard Shipping\",\"description\":\"3-5 business days\",\"cost\":15},{\"type\":\"local_pickup\",\"name\":\"Local Pickup\",\"description\":\"Pick up from our location\",\"warehouse_ids\":[\"main-warehouse-id\"]}]',0,'calculated',0.00,'apsystems-ecu-r-communications-gateway-ecu-r',1,'2025-07-10 20:29:56','2025-10-07 03:37:53'),('a9280e6f-719b-11f0-9a85-0637a5b9918d','Enphase Envoy-S Metered Communications Gateway for Microinverters','',250.00,NULL,NULL,'b5ef143e-4e72-11f0-bbc5-06479488ad4b','ENV-S-AM1-120',0.00,'[]',0,'calculated',0.00,'enphase-envoy-s-metered-communications-gateway-for-microinverters-env-s-am1-120',0,'2025-08-05 01:29:42','2025-08-06 05:47:51'),('a97803f9-a2b6-11f0-8edc-0637a5b9918d','Pallet of 21 Sunpower 425 Watt Solar Panels - Free Shipping!','',1900.00,NULL,'/uploads/datasheets/1759756761753-m6d4r8pcin.pdf','a0b3eb1a-4e72-11f0-bbc5-06479488ad4b','sunpower-425-pallet',0.00,'[{\"type\":\"free\",\"name\":\"Standard Shipping\",\"description\":\"3-5 business days\"},{\"type\":\"local_pickup\",\"name\":\"Local Pickup\",\"description\":\"Pick up from our location\",\"warehouse_ids\":[\"main-warehouse-id\",\"east-warehouse-id\",\"41ee39d4-51d5-11f0-bbc5-06479488ad4b\"]}]',1,'fixed',0.00,'pallet-of-21-sunpower-425-watt-solar-panels-free-shipping-sunpower-425-pallet',0,'2025-10-06 13:16:25','2025-11-17 04:46:27'),('aef44f66-b3e6-11f0-9ae1-0637a5b9918d','EG4 Enclosed Battery Rack | 3 Slot | Wheels Included','<p>EG4 Storage Solutions 3 Slot Battery Rack, featuring an&nbsp;<strong>enclosed cabinet design</strong>. The cabinet door swings open on a sturdy hinge, allowing easy access to the equipment and cables for easy installation. The door panel locks securely to help prevent damage, tampering, and/or theft. The front and back panels are vented, allowing air to flow freely and keeping equipment cool. Top ports allow for easy cable routing.</p><p>The Rack comes fully assembled and ready to roll (with casters, of course, making it a mobile-ready rack). The casters are removable for easy stacking of the enclosure cabinets. Castors and hardware come inside the rack and then are simply bolted on out of the box.</p><p><strong>Included:</strong><br>Assembled EG4 3 Slot Battery Rack + Castors</p><p><strong>Key Features:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Constructed from heavy-duty steel</p></li><li><p>Durable black powder-coated finish</p></li><li><p>Heavy-duty 300A bus bars with protective covers</p></li><li><p>Compatible with all EG4 Server Rack Batteries</p></li><li><p>Dimensions (WxDxH): 23.6 in x 26.8 in x 29.6 in</p></li></ul>',680.00,NULL,'/uploads/datasheets/1761646314837-el4e2o45yok.pdf','a98c7b21-4e72-11f0-bbc5-06479488ad4b','1511229',0.00,'[]',0,'calculated',0.00,'eg4-enclosed-battery-rack-3-slot-wheels-included-1511229',1,'2025-10-28 10:13:00','2025-10-28 10:15:34'),('b0d84ade-a3ef-11f0-8edc-0637a5b9918d','EG4 18kPV Hybrid Inverter','<p>The EG4 18kPV merges grid-tied and off-grid functions into one powerhouse hybrid inverter, eliminating the need for charge controllers or transformers. Certified for common electrical standards, it delivers up to 12,000W of continuous output while seamlessly integrating solar, battery storage, and grid power. Perfect for homes, RVs, and off-grid projects, it can even serve as a backup power source without solar. Enjoy remote monitoring, a sleek design, and a user-friendly LCD interface for easy control of charging, power priority, and voltage settings.</p><p>With plug-and-play installation, robust certifications, and reliable performance, the EG4 18kPV is built for efficiency, flexibility, and long-term energy independence.</p><p><strong>Key Features:</strong></p><ul><li><p>High Performance Output – 18,000W PV input with 12,000W continuous output, stackable for even greater capacity.</p></li><li><p>All-in-One Design – Combines inverter, power management, and storage integration with simple plug-and-play installation.</p></li><li><p>Versatile Power Management – Manages energy from solar, batteries, and the grid simultaneously with 120/240V split-phase support.</p></li><li><p>Built for Durability – Fully outdoor rated (NEMA 4X/IP65) for all-weather use while avoiding direct sunlight exposure.</p></li><li><p>Certified &amp; Compliant – ETL &amp; cETL certified, meeting UL, CSA, IEEE, NEC, and other national/international safety and grid standards.</p></li><li><p>Remote Monitoring &amp; Control – View live system data, track historical performance, and update firmware from anywhere.</p></li></ul>',4300.00,NULL,'/uploads/datasheets/1759891001255-1rm266upwau.pdf','b5ef143e-4e72-11f0-bbc5-06479488ad4b','EG418KPV12LV',0.00,'[]',0,'calculated',0.00,'eg4-18kpv-hybrid-inverter-eg418kpv12lv',1,'2025-10-08 02:37:10','2025-10-08 02:37:10'),('ba24dd7b-4bcc-11f0-bbc5-06479488ad4b','Solar Panel End Clamp For Standard Unistrut','Solar Panel End Clamp for Standard Unistrut, Aluminum 30mm/35mm Solar Panel Brackets with Nuts Bolts, Solar Panel Mounting Kit for Metal Roof, Tin Roof, Flat Roof, Sheet Roof, Black',3.00,NULL,NULL,'be84ed54-4e72-11f0-bbc5-06479488ad4b','GR285ABT',0.00,NULL,0,'calculated',0.00,'solar-panel-end-clamp-for-standard-unistrut-gr285abt',1,'2025-06-17 22:45:11','2025-06-27 13:27:59'),('bad7404e-a2f3-11f0-8edc-0637a5b9918d','Various Racking','',100.00,NULL,NULL,'be84ed54-4e72-11f0-bbc5-06479488ad4b','Racking',0.00,'[{\"type\":\"free\",\"name\":\"Standard Shipping\",\"description\":\"3-5 business days\"},{\"type\":\"local_pickup\",\"name\":\"Local Pickup\",\"description\":\"Pick up from our location\",\"warehouse_ids\":[\"main-warehouse-id\"]}]',0,'calculated',0.00,'various-racking-racking',1,'2025-10-06 20:33:34','2025-10-06 20:40:08'),('badecce1-7486-11f0-9a75-0637a5b9918d','Tigo PV Module Rapid Shutdown Two Modules 15A 1000W 1500V #484-00252-22','',50.00,NULL,NULL,'b5ef143e-4e72-11f0-bbc5-06479488ad4b','TS4-A-2F',0.00,'[]',0,'calculated',0.00,'tigo-pv-module-rapid-shutdown-two-modules-15a-1000w-1500v-484-00252-22-ts4-a-2f',1,'2025-08-08 18:37:25','2025-08-08 18:37:25'),('be169760-ab6e-11f0-8e1b-0637a5b9918d','Emporia EV Charger | White | Hardwire | J1772','<p><strong>Emporia EV Charger</strong></p><p>The Emporia EV Charger offers efficient and reliable Level 2 charging, providing up to 48 amps with a hardwired setup. Recognized as the best Level 2 EV Charger by leading automotive and lifestyle publications, it ensures your EV is always ready to go.</p><p>Featuring smart charging capabilities, users can customize settings, monitor real-time rates, and manage schedules through the Emporia mobile app. The watertight NEMA Type 4 enclosure ensures safe indoor and outdoor installation.</p><p><strong>Key Features:</strong></p><ul><li><p><strong>Fast &amp; Powerful Charging:</strong> Up to 48 amps with hardwired setup.</p></li><li><p><strong>Smart Charging:</strong> Customize settings, real-time monitoring, and remote management via the Emporia app.</p></li><li><p><strong>Outdoor Rated:</strong> Watertight NEMA Type 4 enclosure for versatile installation.</p></li><li><p><strong>Safety Certified:</strong> UL 2594, FCC, ISED, and Energy Star certifications.</p></li><li><p><strong>Safety Features:</strong> Ground fault interrupt protection, internal temperature monitoring, and surge detection. The charger undergoes self-checks to ensure optimal performance, making it a robust and reliable solution for all-electric vehicle owners.</p></li></ul>',425.00,NULL,'/uploads/datasheets/1760715318899-o50wanw1q1e.pdf','a98c7b21-4e72-11f0-bbc5-06479488ad4b','1653003',0.00,'[{\"type\":\"fixed\",\"name\":\"Standard Shipping\",\"description\":\"3-5 business days\",\"cost\":9.99}]',0,'calculated',0.00,'emporia-ev-charger-white-hardwire-j1772-1653003',1,'2025-10-17 15:34:17','2025-10-17 15:35:38'),('bed2402c-80f6-11f0-8e5b-0637a5b9918d','EG4 FlexBoss21 16 kW Hybrid Inverter','<p><strong>EG4 FlexBOSS21 (V 1.1) Hybrid Inverter | 48V Split Phase | 21kW PV Input</strong></p><p><strong>Versatile and Powerful Hybrid Inverter</strong></p><p>The EG4 FlexBOSS21 (V 1.1) is a versatile 48V split-phase, hybrid inverter/charger that offers the same dependable power as the 18kPV with enhanced flexibility. Powerful enough to start a 5-ton AC unit, the FlexBOSS21 supports 21kW of PV input. Capable of paralleling up to 16 units together, the FlexBOSS21 has an impressive total output of 256kW continuous when using PV input. Three MPPTs give users optimal control over their solar needs, while the updated EG4 monitoring software allows for convenient total remote management, complete with mobile notifications and remote setting. Seamless interaction with GridBOSS gives users control over their entire Energy Storage System (ESS).</p><p><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" class=\"text-blue-600 underline\" href=\"https://signaturesolar.com/eg4-flexboss21-lcd-screen-kit/\"><strong>EG4 FlexBOSS21 LCD Screen Kit</strong></a><strong> sold separately&nbsp;</strong></p><p><strong>Key Features:</strong></p><ul><li><p><strong>Flexible Power Options:</strong> Operate off-grid, with grid support, or sell excess power back to the grid.</p></li><li><p><strong>High PV Input Voltage:</strong> Supports up to 600V DC, allowing reduced cable sizes.</p></li><li><p><strong>Smart Connectivity:</strong> Remote access with Wi-Fi and closed-loop communication with compatible batteries.</p></li><li><p><strong>Safety-First Design:</strong> Includes rapid shutdown, ground fault monitoring, arc-fault protection, and robust safety certifications.</p></li><li><p><strong>UL 1741 Certificate of Compliance</strong></p></li><li><p><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" class=\"text-blue-600 underline\" href=\"https://solarequipment.energy.ca.gov/Home/InverterBatteryList?ManufacturerID=EG4+Electronics+LLC&amp;ModelNameID=-1&amp;Submit=Search&amp;Rows=25\"><strong>CEC Solar Equipment Listing</strong></a></p></li></ul><p><strong>Why Choose EG4 FlexBOSS21?</strong> The FlexBOSS21 combines efficiency, durability, and innovation, making it a top choice for those seeking robust energy solutions. Its advanced monitoring and safety features provide reliable power and peace of mind for residential or commercial installations.</p><p><strong>Elevate Your Energy Solutions Today:</strong> Explore the potential of the EG4 FlexBOSS21 Hybrid Inverter and enhance your energy management system.</p><p><strong>Please Note:</strong></p><ul><li><p>You must purchase a 70A Breaker separately for use with the EG4 18kPV Hybrid Inverter.</p></li><li><p>You must purchase a 50A Breaker separately for use with the EG4 12kPV Hybrid Inverter.</p></li><li><p>A 125A Breaker (sold separately) can be used with either the Smart Port or Gen Port.</p></li></ul><p></p><p><em>Whether it’s your first project or your fifth, our USA-based team is here for you. Lifetime support means you’re never on your own.</em></p>',3800.00,NULL,'/uploads/datasheets/1756045767564-i5p2z53u76a.pdf','b5ef143e-4e72-11f0-bbc5-06479488ad4b','EG4INV240V50AFLXBOSSv1',0.00,'[{\"type\":\"free\",\"name\":\"Free Shipping\",\"description\":\"3-5 business days\"},{\"type\":\"local_pickup\",\"name\":\"Local Pickup\",\"description\":\"Pick up from our location\",\"warehouse_ids\":[\"east-warehouse-id\"]}]',0,'calculated',0.00,'eg4-flexboss21-16-kw-hybrid-inverter-eg4inv240v50aflxbossv1',1,'2025-08-24 14:29:30','2025-09-09 05:35:15'),('c08a32ba-b421-11f0-9ae1-0637a5b9918d','EG4-LifePower4 V2 Lithium Battery | 48V 100AH | Server Rack Battery','<h1><strong>EG4-LifePower4 V2 Lithium Battery | 48V 100AH | Server Rack Battery | UL1973, UL9540A | 10-Year Warranty</strong></h1><p>The EG4 LiFePOWER4 48V V2 battery maintains the sturdy design and high performance of the original model, while adding new features for an improved user experience and better system integration. This Lithium Iron Phosphate (LiFePO4) battery is composed of 16 UL recognized prismatic 3.2V cells in series, offering over 6,000 deep discharge cycles at 80% Depth of Discharge (DoD). It has a nominal voltage of 51.2V, an energy capacity of 5.12kWh, and an internal 100A Battery Management System (BMS).</p><p>The battery supports parallel connections of up to 64 units and includes a 10-year limited warranty. Improved terminal connections make it easier to attach chargers or EMP shields. The LiFePOWER4 48V V2 also features RS485 and CAN bus communication for broader inverter compatibility, along with a new Protocol 6 DIP switch for straightforward and convenient inverter and battery customization. Additionally, the E-Stop (Emergency Stop) rapid shutdown (RSD) functionality ensures fail-safe operation in high-risk environments, and dual on-board fire arrestors provide added peace of mind during operation.</p><p><strong>Key Features:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Tested for over 6,000 deep discharge cycles at 80% Depth of Discharge (DoD)</p></li><li><p>51.2V nominal voltage, 5.12kWh energy capacity, 100Ah charge capacity</p></li><li><p>Internal 100A Battery Management System (BMS),Equipped with BMS communication on/off switch</p></li><li><p>New Protocol 6 DIP switch for convenient inverter and battery customization</p></li><li><p>Supports closed-loop communication of up to 64 batteries in parallel, for a maximum storage capacity of 327.7kWh</p></li><li><p>Enhanced terminal connections with two positive and two negative terminals</p></li><li><p>CAN bus and RS485 ports for communication with a wider range of inverters</p></li><li><p>E-Stop (Emergency Stop) rapid shutdown (RSD) functionality for fail-safe operation in high-risk environments</p></li><li><p>Dual on-board fire arrestors for added safety during operation</p></li><li><p>UL 1973 Recognized Component, UL 9540A (passed), UL 9540 Listed with 18kPV-12LV</p></li></ul>',1470.00,NULL,'/uploads/datasheets/1761671743054-ox8u78dttnj.pdf','a98c7b21-4e72-11f0-bbc5-06479488ad4b','1511105',0.00,'[]',0,'calculated',0.00,'eg4-lifepower4-v2-lithium-battery-48v-100ah-server-rack-battery-1511105',1,'2025-10-28 17:15:50','2025-10-28 17:15:50'),('c0a4e674-51f9-11f0-bbc5-06479488ad4b','JA Solar 255 Watt Solar Panel','<p>Harness the power of the sun with the JAP6 60/255/3BB, a high-performance polycrystalline solar panel designed for <strong>residential, commercial, and utility-scale solar projects</strong>.</p><p><strong>Key Features:</strong></p><ul><li><p><strong>Powerful Output:</strong> This 255-watt panel boasts a high output and a <strong>15.59% conversion efficiency</strong>, meaning it\'s designed to generate significant power for your energy needs. It\'s a great option for <strong>rooftop or ground mount applications</strong>.</p></li><li><p><strong>Built to Last:</strong> The JAP6 60/255/3BB is built for durability and reliability. It\'s certified to withstand <strong>high wind loads (2400Pa) and snow loads (5400Pa)</strong>, making it a robust choice for various weather conditions. It\'s also designed with <strong>high salt and ammonia resistance</strong>.</p></li><li><p><strong>Reliable Quality:</strong> JA Solar is a world-leading manufacturer of high-performance photovoltaic products. The JAP6 60/255/3BB demonstrates this commitment to quality with features like:</p><ul><li><p><strong>Positive power tolerance (0~+5W)</strong></p></li><li><p><strong>100% EL double-inspection</strong> ensuring defect-free modules.</p></li></ul></li><li><p><strong>Comprehensive Certifications:</strong> This panel is certified by various international standards, including IEC 61215, IEC 61730, and UL1703.</p></li><li><p><strong>Superior Warranty:</strong> Enjoy peace of mind with a <strong>10-year product warranty</strong> and a <strong>25-year linear power output warranty</strong>. This warranty guarantees <strong>97.5% of its original output after 25 years</strong>.</p></li><li><p><strong>Low Light Performance:</strong> Designed to offer <strong>outstanding performance in low-light environments</strong>.</p></li><li><p><strong>Clear Anodized Frame:</strong> Features a clear anodized frame for a clean aesthetic.</p></li><li><p><strong>MC4 Connector:</strong> Equipped with a standard MC4 connector for easy installation.</p></li></ul><p><strong>Please note:</strong> The JAP6 60/255/3BB model is no longer available.</p><p><strong>Product Specifications:</strong></p><ul><li><p><strong>Watts (Pmax):</strong> 255 W</p></li><li><p><strong>Dimensions:</strong> 64.96\" x 39.02\" x 1.57\"</p></li><li><p><strong>Weight:</strong> 40.12 lbs</p></li><li><p><strong>Max Power Voltage (VMPP):</strong> 30.29 V</p></li><li><p><strong>Max Power Current (IMPP):</strong> 8.42 A</p></li><li><p><strong>Open Circuit Voltage (VOC):</strong> 37.82 V</p></li><li><p><strong>Short Circuit Current (ISC):</strong> 8.98 A</p></li><li><p><strong>Max System Voltage:</strong> DC 1000 V</p></li><li><p><strong>Cell Type:</strong> Polycrystalline</p></li></ul><p>Consider this reliable and efficient solar panel for your renewable energy needs!</p>',50.00,NULL,'/uploads/datasheets/1750879456753-fuhf9tqb91.pdf','a0b3eb1a-4e72-11f0-bbc5-06479488ad4b','JAP6 60/255/3BB',0.00,'[{\"type\":\"fixed\",\"name\":\"Standard Shipping\",\"description\":\"3-5 business days\",\"cost\":500},{\"type\":\"local_pickup\",\"name\":\"Local Pickup\",\"description\":\"Pick up from our location\",\"warehouse_ids\":[\"main-warehouse-id\"]}]',0,'calculated',0.00,'ja-solar-255-watt-solar-panel-jap6-602553bb',0,'2025-06-25 19:22:36','2025-09-08 21:30:11'),('c0f1f5bf-4c0b-11f0-bbc5-06479488ad4b','EG4 WallMount All Weather Lithium Battery 14.3 kWh','<h1><strong>EG4 WallMount All Weather Lithium Battery | 48V 280Ah | 14.3kWh LiFePO4 | All-Weather Energy Storage | UL1973, UL9540A | 10-Year Warranty</strong></h1><p>Introducing the EG4 WallMount All Weather Battery - the ultimate energy storage solution for all your solar power needs. This cutting-edge 48V 280Ah Lithium Iron Phosphate (LiFePO4) battery redefines reliability and performance, ensuring your power supply remains uninterrupted.</p><p><strong>Key Features:</strong></p><p><strong>Confident Power</strong></p><ul><li><p>10kW delivery, with peak power 10.5kW (10 sec.) &amp; 15.4kW (3 sec.)</p></li><li><p>Constant discharge current – 200A</p></li><li><p>Over 8000 cycles at 80% DOD with an 82.6Mwh lifetime production</p></li></ul><p><strong>Reliable</strong></p><ul><li><p>Smart and intelligent BMS for reliability, efficiency and safety</p></li><li><p>Integrated self-heating features when needed in low temperature</p></li></ul><p><strong>All-Weather Design</strong></p><ul><li><p>Perfect for outdoor applications, built to withstand various weather conditions</p></li><li><p>Integrated self-heating feature ensures optimal battery performance in low temperatures.</p></li><li><p>Weather rated quick connectors (Amphenol)</p></li></ul><p><strong>Safety</strong></p><ul><li><p>Dual onboard fire arrestors offer fail-safe protection</p></li><li><p>Innovative&nbsp;<strong><em>total emergency stop</em></strong> function for instant shutdown by RSD / ESS disconnect / inverter RSD</p></li><li><p>10-year warranty offered by EG4 Electronics.</p></li></ul><p><strong>Seamless Integration</strong></p><ul><li><p>Can pair with any&nbsp; hybrid or off-grid inverter in the market</p></li><li><p>Designed to pair seamlessly with EG4, Victron, Growatt,<br>Megarevo, Luxpower, Deye, and Sol-Ark inverters</p></li><li><p>Onboard LCD touch screen for easy BMS monitoring and communication.</p></li><li><p>Quick connect battery cables for fast, safe, and reliable battery connections.</p></li></ul><p><strong>Comprehensive Certifications</strong></p><ul><li><p>UL9540A Certified, UL1973</p></li><li><p>UL9540 with 18kPV: for PowerPro ESS</p><ul><li><p>CN: 5026744</p></li></ul></li><li><p>Outdoor Rating IP65</p></li></ul><p><strong>Energy Storage System</strong></p><ul><li><p>Optional conduit box addon makes installation with an EG4 18kPV simple</p></li><li><p>Turn any EG4 All Weather Battery into a fully capable Energy Storage System when paired with an EG4 18kPV</p></li><li><p>No thermal monitoring, or ventilation needed</p></li><li><p>No maintenance</p></li></ul><p><strong>Technical Specifications:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Model name: WallMount AllWeather Battery</p></li><li><p>Battery Type: LiFePO4 (Lithium Iron Phosphate, Grade A)</p></li><li><p>Voltage: 48V (Nominal: 51.2V, Float: 54V)</p></li><li><p>Continuous Charge/Discharge Current: 200A (Max)</p></li><li><p>Capacity: 14.3kWh</p></li><li><p>BMS: 200A</p></li><li><p>Weight: 308.6 lbs. / 140Kg</p></li></ul>',3800.00,NULL,NULL,'a98c7b21-4e72-11f0-bbc5-06479488ad4b','WP-16/280-1AWLL',0.00,NULL,0,'calculated',0.00,'eg4-wallmount-all-weather-lithium-battery-143-kwh-wp-16280-1awll',1,'2025-06-18 06:16:21','2025-06-27 13:27:59'),('c1a76700-6c9a-11f0-9be2-0637a5b9918d','Alexus 400 Watt Solar Panel','',77.00,NULL,NULL,'a0b3eb1a-4e72-11f0-bbc5-06479488ad4b','ALEX-400-B54-S',0.00,'[]',0,'calculated',0.00,'alexus-400-watt-solar-panel-alex-400-b54-s',0,'2025-07-29 16:40:37','2025-12-13 13:14:17'),('c2b4246e-b383-11f0-9ae1-0637a5b9918d','Q CELLS 380 Watt Solar Panel','<p>380 Watt Solar Module, Q.PEAK-DUO-G9+ Series, 6 × 22 Monocrystalline Q.ANTUM Solar Half Cells, 72.4\" x 40.1\" x 1.26\" (Including Frame), 43 lbs., Black on Black</p><p>The Q.PEAK DUO BLK ML-G9+ features cells powered by Q CELLS\' zero gap Q.ANTUM DUO Z Technology, offering higher module power density and improved all-black aesthetics. By eliminating the gaps between cells, module efficiency is increased in relative terms by 4%, delivering and overall efficiency of up to 20.6%. The numbers of cells contained within the module are increased from 120 half-cells to 132 half-cells. The module is also backed by a 25-year product and performance warranty that guarantees at least 86% of the initial power after 25 years.</p><p><strong>Also known as: </strong>Q.PEAK-DUO-BLK-ML-G9+380</p><p><strong>Specification</strong></p><table class=\"table-auto border-collapse border border-gray-300\" style=\"min-width: 50px\"><colgroup><col style=\"min-width: 25px\"><col style=\"min-width: 25px\"></colgroup><tbody><tr class=\"\"><td class=\"border border-gray-300 p-2\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p>Length</p></td><td class=\"border border-gray-300 p-2\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p>72.4in</p></td></tr><tr class=\"\"><td class=\"border border-gray-300 p-2\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p>Width</p></td><td class=\"border border-gray-300 p-2\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p>40.6in</p></td></tr><tr class=\"\"><td class=\"border border-gray-300 p-2\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p>Rated Power Output</p></td><td class=\"border border-gray-300 p-2\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p>380 W</p></td></tr><tr class=\"\"><td class=\"border border-gray-300 p-2\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p>Voltage (VOC)</p></td><td class=\"border border-gray-300 p-2\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p>45.04V</p></td></tr><tr class=\"\"><td class=\"border border-gray-300 p-2\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p>Number of cells</p></td><td class=\"border border-gray-300 p-2\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p>132</p></td></tr><tr class=\"\"><td class=\"border border-gray-300 p-2\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p>Cell Type</p></td><td class=\"border border-gray-300 p-2\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p>Monocrystalline</p></td></tr><tr class=\"\"><td class=\"border border-gray-300 p-2\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p>Rated Efficiency</p></td><td class=\"border border-gray-300 p-2\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p>20.1%</p></td></tr><tr class=\"\"><td class=\"border border-gray-300 p-2\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p>Connector Type</p></td><td class=\"border border-gray-3