class=\"border border-gray-300 p-2\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p>Solar Panels for Buildings</p></td></tr><tr class=\"\"><td class=\"border border-gray-300 p-2\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p>Use</p></td><td class=\"border border-gray-300 p-2\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><ul><li><p>Commercial</p></li><li><p>Grid-Tie</p></li><li><p>Off-Grid</p></li><li><p>Residential</p></li></ul></td></tr><tr class=\"\"><td class=\"border border-gray-300 p-2\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p>Warranty</p></td><td class=\"border border-gray-300 p-2\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p>25 Year Product and Performance Warranty</p></td></tr></tbody></table>',2100.00,NULL,NULL,'a0b3eb1a-4e72-11f0-bbc5-06479488ad4b','SPR-P19-390-COM-PALLET',0.00,'[{\"type\":\"free\",\"name\":\"Standard Shipping\",\"description\":\"3-5 business days\"},{\"type\":\"local_pickup\",\"name\":\"Local Pickup\",\"description\":\"Pick up from our location\",\"warehouse_ids\":[\"main-warehouse-id\",\"east-warehouse-id\"]}]',1,'fixed',0.00,'pallet-of-23-sunpower-390-watt-solar-panels-spr-p19-390-com-pallet',1,'2025-11-17 03:23:35','2025-12-03 16:19:23'),('d54e8e0d-cf1b-11f0-9923-0637a5b9918d','Installation','',1.00,NULL,NULL,NULL,'Installation',0.00,'[]',0,'calculated',0.00,'installation-installation',1,'2025-12-02 01:11:29','2025-12-15 17:13:01'),('d943b475-be53-11f0-9ad4-0637a5b9918d','SnapNrack | TopSpeed Original with SpeedSeal+ | Solar Panel Roof Mount KIT (1 Mount and 1 Clamp)','<p>The TopSpeed® Original Mount with SpeedSeal+ combines SnapNrack’s proven railless mount with their SpeedSeal+ butyl gasket technology for a clean, reliable seal on comp shingle roofs—without the mess of traditional sealant. It delivers the same install process as the standard TopSpeed Original Mount, now with a pre-applied gasket that simplifies sealing while maintaining long-term weather resistance. Ideal for installers who want a faster, cleaner rooftop experience—without sacrificing performance.&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Key Benefits:</strong>&nbsp;</p><ul><li><p>SpeedSeal+ butyl gasket seals on contact—no sealant required</p></li><li><p>Same install process as standard TopSpeed Original</p></li><li><p>Vertical adjustment slot for fast, easy leveling</p></li><li><p>Compatible with TopSpeed Links and MLPE Mounts<br></p></li><li><p>Supports SnapNrack grounding and wire management solutions</p></li></ul>',19.00,NULL,'/uploads/datasheets/1762792957985-et25cqeup1.pdf','be84ed54-4e72-11f0-bbc5-06479488ad4b','16180042',0.00,'[{\"type\":\"fixed\",\"name\":\"Standard Shipping\",\"description\":\"3-5 business days\",\"cost\":10}]',0,'calculated',0.00,'snapnrack-topspeed-original-with-speedseal-solar-panel-roof-mount-kit-1-mount-and-1-clamp-16180042',1,'2025-11-10 16:39:38','2025-12-11 06:08:20'),('df924ee1-8e79-11f0-95d2-0637a5b9918d','EG4 Chargeverter - GC | 48V 100A Battery Charger 5120W Output','<h1><strong>EG4 Chargeverter - GC | 48V 100A Battery Charger 5120W Output | 240/120V Input</strong></h1><p>Introducing the EG4 Chargeverter 5KW AC Charger, a high-performance battery charger designed for reliability and versatility. With its 48V 100A capacity and 5120W output, this charger ensures efficient power supply for various applications. Its compact design and dual 240/120V input make it suitable for diverse setups.</p><p><strong>Bad Weather Resilience:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Charge batteries during low light conditions using a generator (up to 100A)</p></li><li><p>Ideal for unpredictable weather patterns</p></li></ul><p><strong>Protection from \"Dirty Power\":</strong></p><ul><li><p>Guards against unreliable sine waves from lower-budget generators</p></li><li><p>Protects inverters from power quality issues</p></li></ul><p><strong>Charger Output Specifications:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Optimized for 240 VAC power supply</p></li><li><p>Nominal Battery Voltage: 48VDC</p></li><li><p>Adjustable Charge Current: 0-100A at 240VAC</p></li><li><p>Adjustable Charge Voltage: 43-57VDC (Default at 54VDC)</p></li><li><p>Maximum Output Watts: 5120W at 240 VAC</p></li></ul><p><strong>AC Input Specifications:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Plug directly into a generator without concern for power issues</p></li><li><p>AC Input Voltage Range: 90-264VAC</p></li><li><p>Maximum Input Amps: 26A at 240VAC, 28A at 120VAC</p></li></ul><p><strong>Dry Contacts:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Control of generator start/stop function based on Voltage or state of charge (SOC)</p></li></ul><p><strong>Using EG4 Batteries?</strong></p><ul><li><p>Closed loop communication with EG4 batteries for charging based on battery state of charge (SOC), when batteries are not in communication with the inverter</p></li></ul>',650.00,NULL,'/uploads/datasheets/1757532156224-gp2gx1cm6bd.pdf','b5ef143e-4e72-11f0-bbc5-06479488ad4b','EG4CV48V100AV3',0.00,'[{\"type\":\"free\",\"name\":\"Standard Shipping\",\"description\":\"3-5 business days\"}]',0,'calculated',0.00,'eg4-chargeverter-gc-48v-100a-battery-charger-5120w-output-eg4cv48v100av3',1,'2025-09-10 19:10:54','2025-09-10 19:23:52'),('e16e4b13-73d8-11f0-9985-0637a5b9918d','SolarEdge 10 kW Single Phase Inverter','',500.00,NULL,NULL,'b5ef143e-4e72-11f0-bbc5-06479488ad4b','SE 10000H-US000BNC4',0.00,'[]',0,'calculated',0.00,'solaredge-10-kw-single-phase-inverter-se-10000h-us000bnc4',0,'2025-08-07 21:52:58','2025-08-07 22:34:48'),('e344872b-b415-11f0-9ae1-0637a5b9918d','Mixed Clear 300-350 Watt Solar Panel','<p>These are various solar panels</p><table class=\"table-auto border-collapse border border-gray-300\" style=\"min-width: 100px\"><colgroup><col style=\"min-width: 25px\"><col style=\"min-width: 25px\"><col style=\"min-width: 25px\"><col style=\"min-width: 25px\"></colgroup><tbody><tr class=\"\"><td class=\"border border-gray-300 p-2\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p><strong>Panel</strong></p></td><td class=\"border border-gray-300 p-2\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p><strong>Condition</strong></p></td><td class=\"border border-gray-300 p-2\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p><strong>Quantity</strong></p></td><td class=\"border border-gray-300 p-2\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p><strong>Price Per Panel</strong></p></td></tr><tr class=\"\"><td class=\"border border-gray-300 p-2\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p>Jinko 320</p></td><td class=\"border border-gray-300 p-2\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p>New</p></td><td class=\"border border-gray-300 p-2\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p>26</p></td><td class=\"border border-gray-300 p-2\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p>80</p></td></tr><tr class=\"\"><td class=\"border border-gray-300 p-2\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p>Silfab 330</p></td><td class=\"border border-gray-300 p-2\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p>New</p></td><td class=\"border border-gray-300 p-2\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p>18</p></td><td class=\"border border-gray-300 p-2\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p>80</p></td></tr><tr class=\"\"><td class=\"border border-gray-300 p-2\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p>Axitec 330</p></td><td class=\"border border-gray-300 p-2\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p>New</p></td><td class=\"border border-gray-300 p-2\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p>30</p></td><td class=\"border border-gray-300 p-2\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p>80</p></td></tr><tr class=\"\"><td class=\"border border-gray-300 p-2\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p>Aptos 330</p></td><td class=\"border border-gray-300 p-2\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p>New</p></td><td class=\"border border-gray-300 p-2\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p>18</p></td><td class=\"border border-gray-300 p-2\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p>80</p></td></tr><tr class=\"\"><td class=\"border border-gray-300 p-2\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p>Qcell 320</p></td><td class=\"border border-gray-300 p-2\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p>New</p></td><td class=\"border border-gray-300 p-2\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p>6</p></td><td class=\"border border-gray-300 p-2\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p>80</p></td></tr></tbody></table>',80.00,NULL,NULL,'a0b3eb1a-4e72-11f0-bbc5-06479488ad4b','mixed-cleear-energy-300-350',0.00,'[{\"type\":\"fixed\",\"name\":\"Standard Shipping\",\"description\":\"3-5 business days\",\"cost\":30},{\"type\":\"local_pickup\",\"name\":\"Local Pickup\",\"description\":\"Pick up from our location\",\"warehouse_ids\":[\"main-warehouse-id\"]}]',0,'calculated',0.00,'mixed-clear-300-350-watt-solar-panel-mixed-cleear-energy-300-350',1,'2025-10-28 15:50:54','2025-10-30 22:08:33'),('e387f290-520f-11f0-bbc5-06479488ad4b','Growatt 7.6 kW Hybrid Inverter','<h1><strong>Growatt 7.6kW Grid-Tie Inverter | MIN 7600TL XH-US</strong></h1><h2><strong>Key Features:</strong></h2><h3><strong>Cutting-Edge Grid-Tie:</strong></h3><ul><li><p>7600W nominal output.<br></p></li><li><p>High 500 VDC input!<br></p></li><li><p>3 MPP trackers, 2 strings per MPP tracker.<br></p></li><li><p>Up to 98.5% efficiency!</p></li></ul><h3><strong>Quality Design:</strong></h3><ul><li><p>–13°F to +140°F operating temperature.<br></p></li><li><p>Natural convection cooling.<br></p></li><li><p>NEMA4X (IP65) rated.<br></p></li><li><p>‘Aerospace grade’ flame-retardant lightweight materials.</p></li></ul><h3><strong>Communication:</strong></h3><ul><li><p>4G/Wi-Fi communication with APP, IoT integrated cloud and monitoring.<br></p></li><li><p>IOS, Android &amp; Windows Apps.</p></li></ul><h3><strong>Advanced Protection &amp; Safety:</strong></h3><ul><li><p>UL certified (1741).<br></p></li><li><p>Type III AC surge protection.<br></p></li><li><p>AC short circuit protection.<br></p></li><li><p>Ground fault &amp; grid monitoring.<br></p></li><li><p>AFCI protection.<br></p></li><li><p>Rapid shutdown capable, RFCI protection.<br></p></li><li><p>Anti-islanding protection.<br></p></li><li><p>Residual-current monitoring.</p></li></ul>',500.00,NULL,'/uploads/datasheets/1750889122526-tqij0hvq7c.pdf','b5ef143e-4e72-11f0-bbc5-06479488ad4b','MIN 7600 TL-XH-US',0.00,'[]',0,'calculated',0.00,'growatt-76-kw-hybrid-inverter-min-7600-tl-xh-us',1,'2025-06-25 22:01:04','2025-08-07 02:17:54'),('e5b2b97b-80f5-11f0-8e5b-0637a5b9918d','EG4 GridBOSS MID v3.1','<p><strong>EG4 GridBOSS MID | 200A Microgrid Interconnect Device</strong></p><p>The EG4 GridBOSS MID sets a new standard in microgrid interconnection. Designed to streamline complex solar and backup installations, it combines multiple components into a single, intelligent unit—reducing equipment costs and installation time. With four smart ports, a 200A service entrance rating, and seamless integration with up to three hybrid inverters and a generator, the GridBOSS offers unmatched control, flexibility, and reliability for whole or partial home backup systems.</p><p><strong>Note:</strong><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" class=\"text-blue-600 underline\" href=\"https://signaturesolar.com/gridboss-breaker-kit/?searchid=1575548&amp;search_query=EG4+GridBOSS+BSB+Breaker+Kit\"> Breakers for smart ports, hybrid inverters, and generator input are <strong>sold separately.</strong></a></p><h3><strong>Key Features &amp; Benefits</strong></h3><ul><li><p><strong>Simplified System Integration</strong> – Provides a single connection point for utility power, hybrid inverters, generator, smart loads, and essential/non-essential circuits.</p></li><li><p><strong>Cost-Effective Design</strong> – Lowers equipment and labor costs, saving up to $7,500 in a typical installation.</p></li><li><p><strong>200A Service Entrance Rating</strong> – Delivers full 200A capacity for both backed-up and non-backed-up loads.</p></li><li><p><strong>Smart Load Support</strong> – Includes four configurable ports (125A, 80A, 60A, 60A) for smart loads or AC coupling.</p></li><li><p><strong>Advanced Load Management</strong> – Features five programmable drivers for precise energy distribution.</p></li><li><p><strong>Monitoring &amp; Compatibility</strong> – Supports up to three 90A hybrid inverters, a 125A generator, and eight energy monitoring circuits.</p></li><li><p><strong>Optimized for EG4 Ecosystems</strong> – Pairs seamlessly with the FlexBOSS21 to simplify installations and reduce costs.</p></li></ul>',1880.00,NULL,'/uploads/datasheets/1756045421970-kc4i7fiiqpi.pdf','b5ef143e-4e72-11f0-bbc5-06479488ad4b','EG4MID2P200AV3',0.00,'[{\"type\":\"free\",\"name\":\"Free Shipping\",\"description\":\"3-5 business days\"},{\"type\":\"local_pickup\",\"name\":\"Local Pickup\",\"description\":\"Pick up from our location\",\"warehouse_ids\":[\"east-warehouse-id\"]}]',0,'calculated',0.00,'eg4-gridboss-mid-v31-eg4mid2p200av3',1,'2025-08-24 14:23:25','2025-10-29 21:34:31'),('e6d2bd21-72f0-11f0-9985-0637a5b9918d','LG 16H Prime Battery | 16kWh | 400V | High Voltage','<h2><strong>LG RESU16H Prime – High-Voltage 16kWh Lithium Battery for Home Energy Storage</strong></h2><p>The <strong>LG RESU16H Prime</strong> is a high-capacity, high-voltage lithium-ion battery designed to provide efficient and scalable energy storage for residential applications. With a <strong>16kWh capacity</strong>, it delivers reliable backup power, energy savings, and greater energy independence.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><h3><strong>Key Features and Benefits</strong></h3><ul><li><p><strong>Reliable Backup Power</strong> – Provides <strong>16kWh of stored energy</strong>, enough to keep your home or business running during outages.</p></li><li><p><strong>High-Voltage Efficiency</strong> – Operates at <strong>400V</strong>, allowing for faster charging and better energy conversion compared to lower-voltage batteries.</p></li><li><p><strong>Expandable Storage</strong> – Need more power? <strong>Parallel two batteries</strong> to increase your total capacity to <strong>32kWh</strong>, providing extended backup and energy storage.</p></li><li><p><strong>Long-Lasting Performance</strong> – Uses <strong>advanced lithium-ion technology</strong> for a longer lifespan and higher efficiency than traditional batteries.</p></li><li><p><strong>Built for Safety and Durability</strong> – The <strong>Battery Management System (BMS)</strong> protects against overheating, overcharging, and short circuits.</p></li><li><p><strong>Indoor and Outdoor Ready</strong> – Designed to withstand various conditions for flexible installation options.</p></li><li><p><strong>Smart Energy Use</strong> – Store solar energy for nighttime use or when electricity rates are highest, helping to lower your energy costs.</p></li></ul><p><strong><em>This battery is not compatible with 48V systems or EG4 inverters. Always verify inverter compatibility before purchase.</em></strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><h3><strong>Applications and Use Cases</strong></h3><ul><li><p><strong>Home &amp; Light Commercial Backup Power</strong> – Keep essential appliances, HVAC systems, and refrigeration running during outages.</p></li><li><p><strong>Solar Energy Storage</strong> – Maximize self-consumption by storing excess solar energy for later use.</p></li><li><p><strong>Peak Load Management</strong> – Reduce reliance on the grid by using stored power when demand (and electricity rates) are highest.</p></li><li><p><strong>EV Charging Support</strong> – Store energy for EV charging, minimizing strain on the grid.</p></li><li><p><strong>Commercial &amp; Retail Power</strong> – Reliable backup for refrigeration, lighting, and essential business operations.</p></li></ul><p>&nbsp;</p><h3><strong>Why Choose the LG RESU16H Prime?</strong></h3><p>With its high-voltage design, advanced lithium-ion technology, and expandable capacity, the LG RESU16H Prime offers a reliable and efficient solution for homeowners looking to optimize their energy use. Whether for backup power, energy savings, or greater independence from the grid, this battery delivers long-term value and performance.</p><p>Ready to transform your home energy system? <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" class=\"text-blue-600 underline\" href=\"https://signaturesolar.com/blog/unlocking-the-lg-16h-prime-high-voltage-solar-battery-for-your-home/\">Explore the LG RESU16H Prime today</a>!</p>',2900.00,NULL,NULL,'a98c7b21-4e72-11f0-bbc5-06479488ad4b','16H-Prime',0.00,'[{\"type\":\"free\",\"name\":\"Standard Shipping\",\"description\":\"3-5 business days\"}]',0,'calculated',0.00,'lg-16h-prime-battery-16kwh-400v-high-voltage-16h-prime',1,'2025-08-06 18:12:23','2025-08-07 00:11:03'),('e9ad48af-c213-11f0-9ad4-0637a5b9918d','SnapNrack | TopSpeed™ | Smart Clip II','<p>Module frame cable clip, holds&nbsp;two&nbsp;PV wires of Enphase IQ-Cables. Smart Clips secure wires at any point along the module by tucking wires away within the module frames to avoid any unintended removal over time</p>',0.80,NULL,NULL,'be84ed54-4e72-11f0-bbc5-06479488ad4b','16180022',0.00,'[]',0,'calculated',0.00,'snapnrack-topspeed-smart-clip-ii-16180022',1,'2025-11-15 11:12:02','2025-11-15 11:15:30'),('f014aa2b-9439-11f0-95d2-0637a5b9918d','EG4 280Ah All Weather Conduit Box','',125.00,NULL,NULL,'b5ef143e-4e72-11f0-bbc5-06479488ad4b','Conduit-box',0.00,'[]',0,'calculated',0.00,'eg4-280ah-all-weather-conduit-box-conduit-box',0,'2025-09-18 02:48:21','2025-09-18 02:53:25'),('f225a774-85e3-11f0-9a5f-0637a5b9918d','SolarEdge 3.8 kW Inverter','',300.00,NULL,NULL,'b5ef143e-4e72-11f0-bbc5-06479488ad4b','Solaredge3800',0.00,'[]',0,'calculated',0.00,'solaredge-38-kw-inverter-solaredge3800',1,'2025-08-30 20:57:31','2025-09-30 01:24:10'),('f87b2c28-4bb0-11f0-bbc5-06479488ad4b','Jinko 405 Watt Silver Solar Panel','',60.00,NULL,NULL,'a0b3eb1a-4e72-11f0-bbc5-06479488ad4b','JKM405M-72HL-V',0.00,'[{\"type\":\"fixed\",\"name\":\"Standard Shipping\",\"description\":\"3-5 business days\",\"cost\":500},{\"type\":\"local_pickup\",\"name\":\"Local Pickup\",\"description\":\"Pick up from our location\",\"warehouse_ids\":[\"east-warehouse-id\"]}]',0,'calculated',0.00,'jinko-405-watt-silver-solar-panel-jkm405m-72hl-v',0,'2025-06-17 19:26:30','2025-10-25 16:51:00'),('f941a678-b44a-11f0-9ae1-0637a5b9918d','EG4 12kPV Hybrid Inverter','<h2><strong>EG4 12kPV Hybrid Inverter: The Ultimate Power Solution for Rural and Suburban Homeowners</strong></h2><p>Introducing the <strong>EG4 12kPV Hybrid Inverter</strong>, a pinnacle of innovation and efficiency in solar power technology. This 48V, split-phase hybrid inverter is perfect for rural and suburban homeowners seeking energy independence. Seamlessly integrating into existing systems, it offers unmatched performance and versatility for both residential and light commercial applications. Sharing the same architecture and firmware as the EG4 18kPV, it powers loads and charges batteries efficiently, maximizing your solar energy investment.<br></p><h3><strong>Key Features:</strong></h3><ul><li><p><strong>8kW Continuous Output &amp; Scalable Power</strong> – Delivers reliable energy for homes or small businesses, with the ability to parallel up to 10 units for 80kW total capacity.</p></li><li><p><strong>High Solar Input Capability</strong> – MPPTs rated to 12kW (max 15kW array) with dual high-voltage (120–500 VDC) and high-amperage (25A) inputs for efficient energy conversion.</p></li><li><p><strong>Hybrid Split Phase Design</strong> – Supports off-grid, grid-tied with battery backup, and generator input for versatile power solutions.</p></li><li><p><strong>Load &amp; Surge Handling</strong> – Manages up to a 4,000W imbalance for 30 minutes and 134A surge capacity for demanding applications.</p></li><li><p><strong>Fast &amp; Safe Power Switching</strong> – 10ms transfer time with RSD/ESS shutdown compliance to protect equipment and meet safety standards.</p></li><li><p><strong>Advanced Monitoring &amp; Control</strong> – EG4 app/website for system performance tracking, updates, battery monitoring, and export-limiting applications.</p></li></ul><h3><strong>Why Choose the EG4 12kPV Hybrid Inverter?</strong></h3><p>The EG4 12kPV Hybrid Inverter combines advanced technology with exceptional reliability for residential and light commercial systems. Its high-frequency split-phase design, rapid transfer times, and smart monitoring deliver unmatched performance and flexibility—whether you install a single unit or link up to 10 for a large-scale setup.</p><p>Enjoy robust power output, seamless energy management, and the freedom to go off-grid, stay grid-tied, or sell excess power back. The EG4 12kPV is your dependable, future-ready solar solution.</p>',3600.00,NULL,'/uploads/datasheets/1761689440385-apwsw0c3pvn.pdf','b5ef143e-4e72-11f0-bbc5-06479488ad4b','1511096',0.00,'[]',0,'calculated',0.00,'eg4-12kpv-hybrid-inverter-1511096',1,'2025-10-28 22:10:55','2025-10-28 22:10:55');
